# Git Authorship (Cloud Agent)

## Author identity

All commits made by the agent in this workspace MUST use:

- **Name:** Adrianno E. S.
- **Email:** adriannoes@users.noreply.github.com

Verify before push:

```bash
git config user.name
git config user.email
git log -1 --format=fuller
```

## Co-authors

- **NEVER** add `Co-authored-by:` trailers unless the user explicitly asks in the current chat.
- After every commit, confirm the message has no `Co-authored-by` line.

## Commit workflow

1. Use `git commit --no-verify` when hooks would inject co-authors or wrong identity.
2. Inspect `git log -1 --format=fuller` before `git push`.
3. If author shows `Cursor Agent`, amend with `--author="Adrianno E. S. <adriannoes@users.noreply.github.com>"` before pushing.
